%section.how-to#HowToInstall
  %h2 How To Install
  %p Installing artoo for beaglebone is pretty easy using ruby gems.
  :markdown
        :::bash
        gem install artoo-beaglebone

%section.how-to#HowToUse
  %h2 How to use
  %p This small program causes an LED to blink.
  :markdown
        :::ruby
        require 'artoo'

        connection :beaglebone, :adaptor => :beaglebone
        device :led, :driver => :led, :pin => :P9_12

        work do
          every 1.second do
            led.on? ? led.off : led.on
          end
        end

